  <num>42-502</num>
  <heading>Fee simple estates — Estates tail abolished.</heading>
  <text>All estates of inheritance, including such as were formerly estates tail, shall be adjudged estates in fee simple.</text>
  <annotations>
    <annotation type="History" doc="Stat. 56-2-ch854" path="§1012">Mar. 3, 1901, 31 Stat. 1350, ch. 854, § 1012</annotation>
    <annotation type="Prior Codifications">1981 Ed., § 45-202.</annotation>
    <annotation type="Prior Codifications">1973 Ed., § 45-802.</annotation>
  </annotations>
</section>
